      public ObsBatracien(int id, Date date, Time heure, Lieu lieu, ArrayList<Observateur> observateurs, int[] resObs, EspeceBatracien lEspece)
      Generate a battracian observed
      Parameters:
      id - id of the observation
      date - date of the observation
      heure - time of the observation
      lieu - location of the observation
      observateur - list of the observers
      resObs - contain the number of adults(resObs[0]), of amplexus (resObs[1]), of tadpoles (resObs[2]) and of egg-layings (resObs[3]).
      lEspece - the frogg' specie
